data.description: $10k seller concession on this amazing single level home nested on a large corner lot with an updated RV parking and covered patio on a large fully fenced backyard. Centrally located close to shopping centers and entertainment. Just renewed with efficient solar system, interior and exterior painting, vinyl windows, granite tile counters and back splash, new laminate flooring and wood fireplace. fridge, washer and dryer are included. No HOA.
